results.description:
A muddy fur spotted with tanned spots, a silent predator stealthily tip-toes across the forest floor. There is a cloud of mystery that surrounds his movements, his nature will always be unpredictable to the visiting citizens.
 
The Leopard was first spotted crouched beside the nala flowing downstream Judi Waterhole, as he lay in wait for a thirsty denizen. Alas, his plans were of no avail as a nearby tigress started calling out to her cubs and the leopard was left with little choice, but to bolt.
